<br>
-Pets summoned from 4, 8 need a magical weapon to hit magic-only critters, like wisps.<br>
<br>
-Pets summoned from 4, 8, 12, and 16 can benefit from weapons that have high base damage (scythe, rusty 2-hander,etc), as the base damage of these weapons is higher then the pet's fist damage.<br>
<br>
-Pets from 24, 29, 34 *require* two 1-H weapons to activate duel-wield, except (perhaps) for the very highest level 34 pet you can summon.<br>
<br>
-Pets from 39+ automatically duel-wield with their fists. <br>
<br>
-All pets can benefit from weapons that proc, for the proc effect.<br>
<br>
So, just give your lowbie pets hard hitting 2-hander rusty weapons from 4th to 16, unless you are hunting wisps or stronger undead, like ghouls that need magic to hit.  For these use any summoned 2-hander.<br>
<br>
At level 24 to 34 give the pet a pair of summoned daggers.<br>
<br>
At 39+, let them fight bare handed, unless you want to give them weapons with proc effects. <p><b>Seek Pyremaker</b><br>
